# SQL Scripts

## Overview

This folder contains the SQL queries developed in BigQuery for the GoOutside Market Performance Dashboard project.

The queries were used to:

* Join multiple business datasets
* Create analytical views for reporting
* Generate key business metrics and KPIs
* Support dashboard development in Looker Studio

The resulting datasets served as the foundation for pivot table analysis in Google Sheets and the final interactive dashboard.


---

## Files

| File                        | Description                                           |
| --------------------------- | ----------------------------------------------------- |
| dashboard_data_model.sql    | Main reporting dataset used for dashboard development |
| market_performance_view.sql | Market-level performance analysis                     |
| product_analysis_view.sql   | Product and category analysis                         |
| kpi_calculations.sql        | KPI and business metric calculations                  |


---

## Notes

* Queries have been formatted and documented for portfolio purposes.
* Sensitive project information and credentials have been removed.
* Table and dataset names may be generalized where necessary.
* The focus of these scripts is business analysis and reporting rather than data engineering or data cleaning.
